The rest of the base appeared to be secure and Lord Perseus lead the team
back toward the command center.  Upon receiving the communication, he left
the group and headed for the entrance.

"Tuscon?  Is that you?" He asked in a friendly tone.

On Mar 29, 2010 3:31 PM, <airly2002@...> wrote:



Talon:

Talon looked from the distance the new comer, altough something changed it
was Tucson; she smiled in a enigmatic way and walking foward she said "i
warned you, nightstrike would be hard to make him confess something"

 *From:* Sandy <magicquartz@...>
*Sent:* Monday, March 29, 2010 9:38 AM


To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com
Subject: Re: The Old Maximal Base/Unicron's come back



While home at the old Maximal Base, Quickstride and Rat Trap see it wise to
keep an eye on what is happening outside the base, while keeping things
casual amongst themselves. Rat Trap looks up at the sky, and notices the
minions hanging about, yet he does not make any moves against them.



" I'll sure be glad when we get these creeps off our backs."

Quick Stride plucks at a few blades ...




--00c09f8fe5d9ce5c130482f9d7d5
